BT
/F1 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
48. 708. Td
(Koheez.ai is a web-based clinical decision support and pharmacy operations management platform serving AHF \(AIDS Healthcare) Tj
T* (Foundation\) pharmacies. Its primary functions are: \(1\) HIV/PrEP drug regimen assessment -- checking drug-drug interactions,) Tj
T* (renal/hepatic contraindications, and generating AI-written clinical summaries; \(2\) operational task management, scheduling, QA) Tj
T* (compliance tracking, and controlled substance inventory for pharmacy directors and staff; and \(3\) automated patient retention) Tj
T* (outreach via SMS and email. It is not an EHR, does not store full patient charts, and does not integrate with an EHR system.) Tj
ET
